items.title: Sports Stadiums Wiki
items.headline: Check out Sports Stadiums Wiki
items.desc: This wiki is about documenting and describing sports stadiums old and new from around the world. It is a very difficult task, and I am nowhere near completed as of now. I would like to share my passion for stadiums with the world. Remember, I am just one guy, and I could use all of the help I can get. Thanks!

items.title: Writing Wiki
items.headline: Write, Read, and Share Short-Stories!
items.desc: Create, Share, Read, and Edit Short-Stories. Get tips from the community, share you ideas. Put your writing skills out there on Writing Wikia. Have an idea for a short story but don't feel you have the necessary skill to write it? Share you idea here or simply get advice from other users, and write it yourself!
